      value: "Madam Yaga: D\u1EEBng l\u1EA1i \u0111i, k\u1EBB mang h\u01A1i th\u1EDF
        c\u1EE7a tro t\xE0n. Ng\u01B0\u01A1i t\xECm \u0111\u1EBFn t\xFAp l\u1EC1u
        r\xE1ch n\xE1t n\xE0y \u0111\u1EC3 t\xECm s\u1EF1 s\u1ED1ng."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: "Player: Aria \u0111ang d\u1EA7n h\xF3a \u0111\xE1. B\xE0 l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
        duy nh\u1EA5t \u1EDF c\xE1i l\xE0ng n\xE0y bi\u1EBFt v\u1EC1 th\u1EE9 t\xE0
        thu\u1EADt \u0111\xF3."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: "Madam Yaga: C\xE1i ch\u1EBFt tr\u1EAFng (Gray Scourge) kh\xF4ng d\u1EC5
        bu\xF4ng tha con m\u1ED3i \u0111\xE2u. Ta c\xF3 th\u1EC3 gi\xFAp ng\u01B0\u01A1i
        k\xECm h\xE3m n\xF3, nh\u01B0ng hi v\u1ECDng l\xE0 th\u1EE9 \u0111\u1EAFt
        \u0111\u1ECF nh\u1EA5t \u1EDF v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t n\xE0y.\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: "Player: T\xF4i s\u1EBD tr\u1EA3 b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 gi\xE1 n\xE0o. Ch\u1EC9
        c\u1EA7n n\xF3i cho t\xF4i bi\u1EBFt t\xF4i ph\u1EA3i l\xE0m g\xEC."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: "Madam Yaga: Linh h\u1ED3n con b\xE9 \u0111ang m\u1EDD nh\u1EA1t d\u1EA7n.
        H\xE3y mang cho ta th\u1EA3o d\u01B0\u1EE3c t\u1EEB Khu R\u1EEBng \u0110ang
        Ch\u1EBFt, r\u1ED3i ch\xFAng ta s\u1EBD xem ng\u01B0\u01A1i d\xE1m hy sinh
        bao nhi\xEAu..."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[0].sentence
      value: "D\u1EEBng b\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111i, l\u1EEF kh\xE1ch. Ng\u01B0\u01A1i
        mang theo m\xF9i c\u1EE7a s\u1EF1 tuy\u1EC7t v\u1ECDng... v\xE0 c\u1EA3 h\u01A1i
        l\u1EA1nh c\u1EE7a c\xE1i ch\u1EBFt."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[1].sentence
      value: "Aria \u0111ang d\u1EA7n h\xF3a \u0111\xE1. B\xE0 l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
        duy nh\u1EA5t \u1EDF ng\xF4i l\xE0ng n\xE0y bi\u1EBFt c\xE1ch ng\u0103n c\u1EA3n
        th\u1EE9 t\xE0 thu\u1EADt \u0111\xF3."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[2].sentence
      value: "L\u1EDDi nguy\u1EC1n H\xF4i T\xE0n kh\xF4ng ch\u1EEBa m\u1ED9t ai.
        Ta c\xF3 th\u1EC3 ch\u1EBF thu\u1ED1c k\xECm h\xE3m n\xF3, nh\u01B0ng c\xE1i
        gi\xE1 kh\xF4ng r\u1EBB \u0111\xE2u."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[3].sentence
      value: "T\xF4i s\u1EBD tr\u1EA3 b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 gi\xE1 n\xE0o. N\xF3i \u0111i,
        b\xE0 c\u1EA7n t\xF4i t\xECm th\u1EE9 g\xEC?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[4].sentence
      value: "T\u1ED1t l\u1EAFm... H\xE3y mang cho ta Huy\u1EBFt Th\u1EA3o t\u1EEB
        Khu R\u1EEBng \u0110ang Ch\u1EBFt. \u0110\u1EEBng \u0111\u1EC3 vong h\u1ED3n
        \u1EDF \u0111\xF3 x\xE9 x\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi tr\u1EDF
        v\u1EC1."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[0].speakerName
      value: Madam Yaga
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[1].speakerName
      value: Player
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[2].speakerName
      value: Madam Yaga
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[3].speakerName
      value: Player
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3232815571585405756, guid: ccfdfbca131b8054cb88f400f0458d8b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: conversation.Array.data[4].speakerName
      value: Madam Yaga
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
